  "body": "### Description\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: when you type more than 2 rows of text or 7 rows of emoji focus goes below input field and all next rows are overlapped by keyboard, so you cannot see what you are typing\r\n![andr_20](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/34386376-fbac5a84-eb30-11e7-8e12-d76e693ffeb8.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nuser can see what he types and top row goes upper input field\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nuser can see what he types and bottom row goes under input field and overlapped by keyboard\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Go to Chats\r\n- Open any chat\r\n- Type text which contains more than 2 rows of text (or 8 emoji rows)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Status version: \r\n is reproducible on current develop 27/12 (0.9.11d486)\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Android\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\nTF session (with text): (01:50 -\r\n 2:20) \r\nhttps://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/7375901/sessions/9/?accessToken=uKmkdE9nlLqNRLqXoHe1N-UHdfE\r\nTF session (with emoji): (0:08 - 01:05)\r\nhttps://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/7375500/sessions/5/?accessToken=XAuk/hwAEY7q5VlI1H9Mz1Cc0Xs",
